Summary: Appeared to be white circular shape objects, but I didn't notice these objects til after I previewed the pictures I had taken.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking on a particular property in Leiper's Fork, TN off of Floyd Rd. I had my camera and began to take several pictures, when I noticed these white objects appeaing on some of the pics & not all of them. I continued to take more and noticed the object again, so i immediately took another soon after. To my surprise, it appeared as if the white object began to move according to the object direction on my pictures. Soon there after, no more objects appeared.
